I’ll share the useful advanced techniques that experienced AI operators use, but I’ll keep them grounded in how the systems actually work. There aren’t really “secret hacks”—just patterns that reliably improve results because of how language models process context.

Below are several additional “control levers” beyond the six we discussed. Together they form a practical toolkit.

